column5: So, does this count or is it cheating??? LOL  <embed src="http://www.ebaumsworld.com/player.swf" allowScriptAccess="always" flashvars="id1=82533698" wmode="opaque" width="567" height="345" allowfullscreen="true"/>
that's insane!! I believe there's a similar video out there with a marlin or sail fish of some sort... needless to say, that guy wasn't so lucky...
No OFC tourney sign, it doesn't count.
He had it, but had to use it to wipe something off....
An extreme example of spring boarding!

Oh oh, the fish are finally fighting back. They have enlisted jihadist 'Cudas on suicide missions. Soon we will need Bush and Cheney to enlist Haliburton to address the situation with counter strike Dolphins all at massive expense.
That would just make it dark meat Joe.  Saw a similar thing happen with a northern pike. The pike only had to clear the gunnels of a tinny but jumped right in the boat. That cuda was suicidal.
If that happened to me, I would need to change my shorts afterward.  So yes, it counts. Yeesh.
